column2: select b.eid, b.Qualifications_#, a.encoding_id, c.value, c.meaning AS # from dbo.Education b cross apply openjson ([Qualifications_#]) join metadata.columninfo a on a.column_name = # AND a.table_name = # And a.encoding_id = # left join metadata.encoding c on c.encoding_id = a.encoding_id AND c.encoding_id = #
